source.name: Cool roofs
source.description: Locations of buildings participating in the Cool Roofs initiative.  NYC Cool Roofs buildings have a reflective surface applied to their rooftop, helping to reduce cooling costs, cut energy usage and lower greenhouse gas emissions.
